description: For sale: $29,000. 2+ bedroom 3/4 bath home situated on a nice 60x160 lot in Soudan only minutes from Lake Vermilion. This home has main floor laundry and new kitchen flooring. The exterior boasts a newer roof and large back deck with sliding glass doors.

description: Recently sold: $92,000. This is a beautiful updated city home on the edge of town, backed right up to the woods where you can view deer, bear and wolves off the back deck.  Enjoy this a 360 degree view with this deck that wraps around all 4 sides of the house.  This home offers two bedrooms, 1.5 baths, a large living room and a large family room will give your family lots of space.  There is also a 16x22 heated workshop for all your project needs.  A new roof, new windows and a beautiful remodeled kitchen with Stainless Steel appliances, have all been added since 2008.
